{"tid":241591,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人真係試過用藥膏醫包莖","createTime":"2017-05-13T09:16:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T09:32:46.000Z","uid":61728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"af941379221b0e03490beb873f0dbef01e6289e6","tid":241591,"uid":61728,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T09:16:41.000Z","msg":"聽人講用裨乃膚可以解決問題<br />\n但係我係嚴重到扯個時只係露到少少龜頭出黎(開口太窄)<br />\n咁其實係唔係冇用<br />\n<br />\n如果真係要做手術，其實有冇手術係可以保留到包皮...<br />\n我聽人講其實有塊皮係舒服100倍<br />\n我成日係度諗如果只係開口窄，咁剪左開口窄個個位留返一半包皮咁唔得架咩?"},{"pid":"740ec0065a773e3e92cf4e4515b6d470ac8ff779","tid":241591,"uid":37610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T09:18:57.000Z","msg":"用多D飛機杯可以醫到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb9c8c90cf1dadd82cd8dedee18cc0ee60a63cc","tid":241591,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T09:19:44.000Z","msg":"感情台？你同塊包皮嘅感情？"},{"pid":"832fa870cbe95972f5bcdd0c28386f9cfc306b96","tid":241591,"uid":61728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T09:23:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>感情台？你同塊包皮嘅感情？</blockquote><br />\n絕對有，同自己身體部份當然有感情"},{"pid":"b095ade546fc2c046683dbee53f54132f5951da6","tid":241591,"uid":41859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T09:24:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>感情台？你同塊包皮嘅感情？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb81c778f6ae3cc9c093961afae067231a6edf2a","tid":241591,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T09:26:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>感情台？你同塊包皮嘅感情？</blockquote><br />\n絕對有，同自己身體部份當然有感情</blockquote><br />\n剪頭髮指甲每每痛哭流涕"},{"pid":"aae282176e0f82afed33420119d6d2d809ec5033","tid":241591,"ui